Merge branch 'master' of https://github.com/nilodna/mestrado

only because my change in readme.md file
mat files with all study case variables
pequenas mudancas no relatorio anual antes da impressao
upload routine to cut grb2 file with cdo
add new function to download CFSR data
changes tidal lag to 12h from original
documentation about the tidal calibration before the break
routines to plot climatology and summers and figures
new pickles and new routine to visualize MERRA-2 data
updating figures and selected periods with v > 0
test case figure edited with colors
new routine to visualize output's file
checking for gridpoints at same location between SBB and CFSv2 grids
altering CFS_GRID to work in tripoli and oceano
new bash script to cut output data
new temp figures and control selection
final routine to perform an EOF analysis [with wu and combined, wu and wv]
adding routines for wind files to model
implementing surface heat flux as force
multiplying data by -1, so we can change DOWNWARD FLUX to UPWARD FLUX
updating routinas to plot cross section
routines for OPTION 3 - meteorological data, spatial and temporal varying
